#Q2
select 
subscriber_type, landmark, start_date
from `bigquery-public-data.san_francisco.bikeshare_trips` a
join `bigquery-public-data.san_francisco.bikeshare_stations` b 
on a.start_station_id = b.station_id
where subscriber_type = "Subscriber"
and landmark = "Redwood City"
and start_date between "2016-07-01" and "2016-12-31";
#result in Q2 = 1
#More people subscribers rented the bicycle in the first quarter of 2016 than in the second quarter of 2016, with 
750 and 1 rentals respectively.
